        <span class="key-hint px-1.5 sm:px-2 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-purple-300">↑</span>
        <span class="key-hint px-1.5 sm:px-2 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-purple-300">W</span>
        <span class="ml-1 font-medium">Boost</span>
